snippet.title: Restless Nights Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Announcement Trailer for my next game titled "Restless Nights"

its been a lot of fun working on this and I can't wait to share it with you all.

Think of this game as a hybrid of FNAF and I'm on Observation Duty, with a dash of Try to Fall Asleep.
